content.detailedDescription:
My ufo experience 				july 2 1978
   
the craft i witnessed was saucer shape and there were lights illuminating around the bottom.  it was very large and right above a drive-in movie, which was having a swap & shop where there were at least 100 people.  i was two blocks away in my front yard and watched with amazement.  i ran up the block and watched the craft as long as i could until it finally went out of site.  i asked people at the swap & shop if they had seen the saucer and no one had seen anything.  i couldn't understand why or how this could be, because it was about as big as the drive in itself.  the saucer was hovering over the drive-in for five minutes or so then moved on west slowly.  my thoughts were it was a blimp or something like that but it looked too real to be a blimp.  it was very real and i seem to be the only one who saw it.  now that is strange.  but true! 

michael house
kansas city, kansas
content.summary: Saucer shape and there were lights illuminating around the bottom

content.detailedDescription: I was jumping in a leaf pile at around 4:00 pm when i heard the sound of a plane. naturally, looked up to see what kind of plane it was. out of the corner of my eye, i noticed a black, metallic object that reflected light ahead of the plane. i thought it was another plane, but it had no wings, was orb-shaped, and seemed to be rotating. it was stationary as the plane flew by. i decided to grab my phone from my pocket to snap a photo so that i had proof to show others. i managed to get the plane in the photo. while the ordeal was occurring, i was a bit scared that i would be abducted, but also intrigued at the fact that the technology must be far more advanced than ours. i decided to run into the house to grab my camera to take a video or at least a high-quality photo. when i had come out, the object had vanished. i never saw the object again.
content.summary: A metallic-like, rotating orb that seemed to hover near an airplane

content.detailedDescription:
2/23/17 approximately 7:10pm central, new caney, texas

i work from home and had taken a break. i went outside on our porch which is about 8 feet off the ground and faces to the west.  it was already dark outside and i saw an unusual light directly in front of me just past the tree line.  i called my husband out because the light was moving and i wanted to make sure my eyes were not playing tricks on me.  we both agreed that the object was moving strangely so i went and got my camera out to video record it.  my son also came out to see the object.  he placed the camera where it would be stationary and you can clearly see side to side and up and down movement, hovering.  at one point which i did not catch on camera, the lights dimmed to a blur, then got bright again.

we did not hear any sounds coming from the object.  in fact, it was extremely quiet outside last night, much more than usual. we live in the country and normally you would be hearing a lot of insects and dogs.

the object was too far for even the camera to make out what it was. the object stayed in the sky for some time as it moved northwest and dropped below the tree line.

i live just four miles from the piney woods incident of 1980 in huffman, texas.
content.flightPath: Hovering then path,Path with directional change,Path then hovering
content.summary: Very bright light, larger than a star, moving side to side and  up and down

content.detailedDescription:
It was about 7:30 pm jan. 2, 2016. it was dark but plenty of light from the city. i am returning from the store on my bicycle. i am moving north very slow. in the ne i see a reddish-orange sphere edges coming my way and slowly descending. its moving slow, about walking speed. if i continue on my bike it looks as though it would pass behind me. i did a slow u-turn and got into it's path. it is about 10 feet away and not much higher than my head while i stand on my peddles. this one is 3-4 feet in diameter. i am almost directly in it's path. it comes to a sudden stop. the part of it facing the ground flipped up and i saw a big eye like the "cbs" logo and again it looked like a jellyfish. sort of like a hood that extends out from the body. to put a human characteristic to it, it looked as though it was surprised when it "noticed" i was there. it stopped and jumped back a little, flipped up, "looked" at me, then shot off to the east. within 1-2 seconds it was a few miles away. it flashed off/on a few times as it went making streaks and changing colors. then it stopped and turned south, the direction of tampa bay, accelerated, flashed making streaks, and changing colors until couldn't see it anymore.
i will make a seperate report for the following..
i was near my house and i hurried to tell my neighbors from the night before. i see the door is open and the lights are on. i lay my bike down in the driveway and when i look up there is a large red-orange sphere 5-10 feet above their house. this is 6-8 feet in diameter. i rush inside to get them. they come outside and the three of us look at it for a few minutes. it ascends and speeds to the south, flashes a few times as it goes, and is gone.

content.detailedDescription: I went outside almost exactly at 12 am jan. 1 2016 to watch the fireworks set off by the people in the neighborhood. i was on my bicycle a few houses away from my own. as the fireworks are finishing i notice a light from the south, moving north. its a glowing reddish-orange sphere. it looks to be coming from the tarpon springs area and very low, not much higher than the trees. its moving slow a little faster than walking speed. i am in it's path so i keep watching to make sure its not a plane or something. as it gets closer i still don't see any flashing lights or steady white lights. it looks to be 6-8 feet in diameter.  as it gets near maybe a 500 feet or less in a blink of an eye its several hundred feet over my head. i move slightly to get directly under it. when i did it looked like the cage that holds the cork on a champagne bottle. sort of jellyfish like without the tentacles. the underside looked like a big eye. like the "cbs" logo. after taking a long look i rushed to the house to get my camera, knowing the thing would not be there when i got back. it took less than a minute but it was gone. when i went out with my cam i noticed my neighbors were outside, also watching the fireworks. they asked what was going on. i asked how long they had been outside and did they see the thing. they did. for a week or two before that night i kept having a thought that said to watch january 1-8. my neighbors and i saw basically the same thing up close the next night as well.
content.summary: Glowing red-orange sphere

content.detailedDescription: A friend and i were traveling south on 574n. in 1972 sometime in the month of june,about 5 or 6 miles north of ruskin fl. when my friend asked me to look out his window and tell him what i thought the object he was looking at was. i appeared to be a very large rectangular object with no shape that we could see, but the lights were in a line. it looked to be about 300 to 500 feet off the ground off to the east. the object stayed with us while we were running about 60 mph and as we got faster it stayed in the same spot, looking through the passenger side window so we slowed down to around 45 mph and we could still see the object in the same spot as it moved with us. after about 5 minutes or so the object turned to a big ball that looked like white hot lava  and left so fast all you could see was a streak that followed it and we thought it was gone and started to talk about what we were going to tell everybody and decided on not saying anything. about that time it came back to the same spot, looking through the window that it was in before it left the first time and turned to the three colors and followed us for about 5 or 6 more miles, just before we got to tampa city limits and turned back to the light ball and left for good.Ruskin fl. is about 27 miles south of tampa fl.
content.flightPath: Hovering then path,Path with directional change,Path then hovering
content.summary: Large white hot ball. turned to colors red green & blue then disappeared, came back then left to s.E. making no noise.

content.detailedDescription: I was coming from shopping, i saw it directly in front of me, stationary, about 100 feet above the horizon. as i continued,i realized it was much higher as i drove under it. i stopped the car to get a picture, and when i got out, it was gone. visibility was about 3 miles in any direction. it was nowhere to be seen. it was not on the ground, not in another direction, not higher up. just gone. at first i thought it was a huge balloon, but it was luminous, and didn't appear to be tethered. it was completely still. the wind was out of the south at about 15 mph, but it was motionless. it looked like an enormous pearl. how did i feel? i felt like i was looking at something unusual.
content.summary: I noticed it directly over head, after about 1 minute, when i got out of the car to take a picture, it was gone.

content.detailedDescription: Outside enjoying a few minutes of beautiful weather on my front porch i looked to the north west.  i saw what appeared to be a plane headed due south out of the minneapolis area airport (we see a lot of them).  moving fast, very fast.  then just stopped.  at first i thought it was turning or climbing, but after watching for 5-10 minutes it's position had not changed.  in between me and the object a helicopter flew over - it's lights were pin pricks compared to the light given off by the object many more miles in the distance.  in addition, i could see several other planes coming out of the minneapolis area and even though several passed closer to me their lights were much smaller and more distinguishable.  planes to the west, further beyond the object could be seen to be turning or changing altitude.  i watched for about 20 minutes until i was needed back inside.  i returned 2-3 times and the object remained in the same location.  about 4 times later - approx. 45 minutes after the first sighting the object was gone.  nothing to be seen in any direction even though i walked out and looked all around from the yard.
content.summary: Very bright fast object much larger than plane lights flew in straight line then just stopped

content.detailedDescription: Husband was walking dogs on our 5 acres after dark. urgently  came in telling myself & our two sons to come look at something.  we went outside wrapped  in blankets since it was cold. stood on left side of front porch. saw a strobe of red/blue lights moving in a clockwise direction in a triangle shape. no noise. just moving lights in a somewhat slow pattern. but continuous. we watched for a good long time. it was too cold. we came back in. i went back outside. the guys followed. we saw a plane coming from a distance to the far right of the object. the triangle & lights continued as before until the plane got very close. then the triangle grew much bigger. after the plane appeared to pass through the location of the triangle then it went back down to the original size. all this time the lights kept going in the same motion without stopping. i joked & said we should call the police. well i did. i reported everything to the wichita county police since we are on the outskirts of iowa park. they asked a few detailed questions. they asked if i wanted an officer to come speak to me. i said no. it was getting late & was in my pajamas. the officer said he would send a police officer out to check it out. we noticed that it stayed in the same exact location for about 3 or 4 hours. that field is usually used for wheat crops. sometimes the local farmer will put his cattle there to graze. it was empty at the time. no cows. at one point  my son tried to use our camcorder  to film it but all we got was static. it wouldn't  come out on the camcorder. i tried to report this online shortly  after it happened  but i used some bogus ufo site. don't  recall the name. never got a call from the police on whether they saw what we saw.
content.summary: Was above open farmland next our acreage. got big as plane approached. returned  to smaller size after plane passed

content.detailedDescription: It was 1976 i believe when my sister, wife, and friend were on our way to bowling league night when we noticed a white light shaped like a saucer hovering over mnt. charleston west of las vegas nv. when we turned the corner onto stewart ave we notice approximately 8 to 10 other cars pulled off the side of the road watching the same light. we pulled over and joined the others. everyone was excited and pumped. several wanted to exchange names and handshakes stating that we were experiencing something that may be a life changing or life long memory together. i immediately told the others in my group to stay with the other people on the side of the road while i drove back to my house to call nellis afb to report it. we didn't have cell phones in those days and i only lived approximately one mile away. when i got home and called the base, the operator at the base answered the phone saying :if you are calling about the ufo, we already know and are scrambling jets as we speak: i said thank you, hung up and returned to the others. when i got there, the light was still there at which time it had a baby white saucer slowly drop down from the large one attached by a beam of light as if it was tethering from the mother saucer. it descended down what looked to be maybe a hundred feet, then moved the same distance to the north and then again dropped down the same distance. all the time still connected to the light tether that remained in the same path it took to get where it was. at that time we heard the nellis jets roaring very loud as they took off in the direction to the ufo. at the jets were headed that way, the baby saucer very slowly followed the light beam tether back up to the mother or large saucer as if it was going into the bottom of it where it descended from. as the jets got where i would guess was 3/4 of the distance to the saucer, the light slowly dissipated. we all gave one another hugs on the side of the road, got in our vehicles respectfully and drove off. there was very little mention on the news the next day other than there was several reports of strange lights last evening over mount charleston. when i mentioned it to others they just blew it off by saying maybe it was the military doing red flag training or something. its been many year ago and i've always wanted to tell some one about it and there it is. my ex wife has since passed away, i've lost tough with my other friend that was with us and my sister lives in rhode island and i'm now in south texas. my sister remembers the incident very well and agreed that i should tell you my story. thanks for reading this and i like what yall do on hanger 1.   cheers
content.summary: Saucer shaped with baby saucer decending from it tethered by beam of light

content.detailedDescription:
My family was traveling home, to wyoming, in the early 1990s.  we were about half way through the state of south dakota, on i-90, when i saw the wide, pie-shaped object, hovering just above a home on the north side of i-90.  i watched the object ascend a very short distance, and move to descend and hover over another home.  i was impressed by this large object, larger than the size of the home, being able to hover so close to the rooftop of two homes.  i did not report it at the time because i thought i would be ridiculed or dismissed by authorities.  i pointed out the object to my husband, who was driving the car, but his main focus was on watching the road in front of him.  he did not see the object ascend and descend over the other home.  i did, however, tell my sister about it, who thought by my description, that i had seen a ufo.  at the time of this siting, the public, to my knowledge, had never seen government aircraft that were shaped like this, and that could hover like this craft did.  i was within 500' of this object, but i did not hear any noise.  trying to justify what i saw, i thought that maybe it was a secret project the air force was testing.

i thought to report this to mufon, once i learned there was an organization like mufon, because i wanted to have mufon possibly provide an explanation of what i saw.  i also want to say that this is the only time i have ever experienced anything like this.
content.summary: Saw it, hovering over two homes, while traveling home to wyoming from wisconsin.

content.detailedDescription: I was driving along the river beside gainsborough highway heading home from picking kids up from church. i always check out the sky on our way in or out of home. we had just came up the hill to the seven sisters,which is a natural formation of rocks the town named. i looked to my right in the sky an where normally would be a few bright stars was a glowing light stationary in the sky. i was driving at least 45-50. i then asked if my step sons noticed the light too,at first i argued that it wasn't a star because i look every night on my way from work an this was the first i had seen the object. i continued home and returned to find that the object had left the area. i think i knew it would not be there when i returned but i felt i had to go back to see. i thought the object mite have been a a military craft but the light was not like lights on air craft it seemed to completely covered in the light emitting from it.
content.summary: A light that would seem like a light bulb on in a house, or a dim search light.

content.detailedDescription: My wife and myself i was driving west on hwy 70.I saw a very,very bright light going east just above the tree tops. we pulled off the road and stopped. i turned off the car and we got out of the car,the object came right over us and slowly disappeared over the trees. it had extremely bright white lights on the frunt, and 2 red lights on the rear. it moved very slowly and there was no sound from it.We got in the car and left. we both were sort of shocked. i was in the usaf and i know it was not an airplane. it moved to slow and made no sound.I have believed in aliens my entire life. i don't know why i didn't check my watch or the car clock. i new i should have,but why i didn't is beyond me. its like we were dazed & confused.
content.summary: We were going west on hwy70 seen very,very bright white light at tree tops stopped car got out it went right over us. made no sound,appeard black very slowly went east.And left still at tree top level .

content.detailedDescription:
About how i got there from my friends' house. se lives near beach in isla verde. the last thing i remember was passing by a landmark (el ltimo trole -"the last trolley") by the beach. next i was parked far away on the side of road #2; a busy main, 4 lane road . about 500 ft. above  me was a craft. it looked like a very large jumbo plane, without wings nor windows, white and self illuminated. it had a straight white beam touching the ground and did not illuminate anything around me. it was just compact ad straight down. it did not touch my car. don't know how long i was there. then the object went straight up without any noise in a second. it flew across the sky to the left. it was bright white and about the size of venus. it stopped when it met with another star-like object and the flew off in a second towards
ne, towards san juan, our capitol. they just disapeared.

 i don't remember getting back on the road. both my daughter and i were calm, as if in a daze. i turned right towards a road which is a shortcut to home. all of a sudden we saw a bright light light coming towards us. we both awoke from that daze and i started shaking so terribly that i could hardly keep my foot on the pedal. we both stared screaming and saying "they've come back for us!" we then noticed it was a plane. then calm returned and when we got home we went to bed and, strangely, did not talk about it for about a year later. it was as if it never happened and it had been wiped from our minds.

i have had things happen since i was a little girl and through my adult life to the present. i have a scar on my right arm from an event when i was about 16 years old. i am a 77 year old great gandmother. other members of my mother's side have also experienced encounters too.

well, that's it. there is so much more, but that's about as much as i'm writing. please keep me anonymous. i have read a lot and seen documentaries. i am terrified for my family and myself of the government's actions towards ordinary people like me. i am not interested in any sort of publicity. i just, after many, many years, decided i should tell my story, before i die, in case it can help others.
content.summary: I was returning home from friend's house with my 15 yr old daughter. i remember nothing after about 2 miles from her home ad found myself parked on the side of the road staring up at this object. it was as if we were hypnotized because we were so calm.

content.detailedDescription: School year of 2013. i was the only one who witnessed it for my family. about 7 o'clock at night it was starting to be winter.I watching tv in my living room. i saw purple lights flash one time,from over the lake in the air. i ran outside to take a closer look.My dog started barking. i went out to my driveway. my driveway is a shared driveway with my neighbor. he was gone. i looked up in the sky moved over to my neighbors side of the driveway. i saw giant triangular dark figure bigger than 4 houses. fly low from the lake over a bunch of houses including mine. and i watched it till i couldn't see it anymore. after i couldn't see it anymore the dog stop the barking. it was pretty close to the rooftops of the houses. close as  within 200 feet from the rooftop of the houses. the craft was long lengthy triangle. it had a narrow tip and a fat back. it made no noise and it flash purple lights once. i tried to take a photo but my phone was dead.
content.summary: Saw a triangular craft with purple lights fly over my house from the lake.

content.detailedDescription: Friend and i fishing an evening friendly bass tournament.3pm-9pm smith and sales reservoir. the fishing picked up as tournament ended. so i convinced my friend to go back out for night bite.Somewhere around 11pm.We were fishing at the end of a penninsula facing the shore with a dark empty house on the land. it was very quit but i thought a helicopter was coming down in the cove behind the house where we couldnt see.But no noise. i gestered to my friend but when the lights dimmed we excused it as a vehicles lights musr have come down the road and backed away.(but we never seen a vehicle) we continued fishing towards the shore in plain view of the house when i noticed what looked like children playing with flaslights moving them frantically in one of the rooms of the house through the windows. my fishing partner and i decided people must have come home to the house (even though we never seen a car or peple) and the power must be turned off in the house. we continued fishing and almost immediately although we never seen or heard anyone, there was an abnormally(7ft) tall human shaped figure witd asmaller child size human shaped figure with the larger one looking like it was holding a flashlight looking for frogs and such at the waters edge. the odd thing was the way they were illuminating, almost like glow in the dark? but we dismissed that as the flashlight reflecting off the water back at them strangely.Just then we notised about 15 to 20 glowing shaped figures all on the shore facing us all different sizes and we got freeked out because there was never any noise this whole time and we were close enough to have heard people walking in the brush near shore.Just as we were getting scared and contimplating leaving, the flashlight the first big human figure was holding shined ddirect towards our boat. my partner said to start the motor and"lets get out of here!"as i was starting to set the choke and pull the cord of the small 5hp outboard motor the flashlight levitated across aboit 30-40yards of water as i was keeping half an eye on it and starting the motor! when it turbed over and i put it in gear, i looked up and the light was about 8feet above our small boat! i never looked back and it was a short 3 minute ride back to the boat ramp. where we hurried throwing the boat in the van and got inside the van in shock. all the dogs on the lake were barking loudly( we never heard a dog before this) my friend made me promise not to tell anyone.And i haven't...Till now
content.summary: Fishing at night with friend.Wierd light came down behind house.Ended with glowing entities at shoreline and getting chased by a flashlight.

content.detailedDescription: My stepmom who was in her seventies and myself were walking the dog. out in the southeastern sky, i noticed the moon. but after a second or two, i realized it was smaller than a full moon and lower in the sky. i said what the heck, and my mom said you see that too? as soon as she said that, the object moved to the north faster than anything we have ever seen. then there was a flash and it was gone. today while watching a hanger 1 show while cleaning, i heard the announcer say a group of ladies in a van and the thing chasing them was orb like. it reminded me of this.  i just wanted someone to know about this. we both were shaking by the time we got home from that walk. it was the most amazing and unusual thing i have ever seen.
content.summary: Thought it was the moon

content.detailedDescription: I was staying in a log cabin with my then partner in a little place called carbeth near glasgow .The cabins had no electricity or running water so we had to collect water from an outside tap and collect firewood and so on .Anyway it was around midnight when my ex partner went outside to bring in firewood for the morning from our supply when he came rushing back inside excitedly saying "come here quickly ,you have to see this "it was unlike him to act like this so i got up and followed him outside .He was looking straight upwards at the sky and i followed his gaze and at first i couldn't see what he was talking about .The night sky was beautiful to look at because carbeth has no street lights or city lights so the stars seem brighter but then he pointed and i focused and it was then i saw it or rather them .In amongst the twinkling stars there were a group of them moving in a co-ordinated fashion .I have tried to describe them to people over the years and the nearest description to the way they moved was like ,you know when you look through a kaleidescope and turn it ? ,well very similar to that .They were very high up in the sky and looked just like the surrounding stars except these were not stars .I have no idea what they were all i know is that i have never seen anything like it before or since ,it was as if they were putting on a display ! i'm guessing that because of how high up they were that they were quite far apart from each other but yet the really weird thing was that they were perfectly in time with each other .Like they all would stop and change direction at exactly the same time .It actually made the hairs on my neck stand up because i know we don't even have space craft that can do what these things were doing .To this day i'm baffled by it .We watched them for i don't know how long but until my neck got sore from looking up ,then eventually we went inside to go to bed but i couldn't sleep ,i couldn't stop thinking " what was that ?"i got up again around an hour later and looked outside again and after a few seconds i spotted them again ,in exactly the same place ! i will never forget what we saw that night .It has made me believe that some intelligence ,something that we don't yet understand exists out there .I saw it with my own eyes .
content.summary: We watched a group of star-like lights  doing crazy manouveres

content.detailedDescription: Yellow glowing ball traveled horizon to horizon with no noise in about 3 minutes
content.summary: Yellow ball no noise solid light
